==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Blasting
<hw>Blast"ing</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A
blast; destruction by a blast, or by some pernicious cause.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>I have smitten you with <qex>blasting</qex> and mildew.</q>
<rj><qau>Amos iv. 9.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The act or process of one who, or that which,
blasts; the business of one who blasts.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Blast lamp</ent>⟦br⟧
